ingredientsDesc:
RF Reagent containing:
Reactive Ingredients
Reagent 1 (R1): None
Reagent 2 (R2): Latex particles coated with human IgG.

Other Ingredients
Reagent 1 (R1): Buffers, inorganic salt, protein, preservative
Reagent 2 (R2): Buffer, inorganic salt, preserative

Calibrator Kit 16: is an aqueous solution containing processed human serum, buffer, protein, inorganic salt, and preservative. 5 leavels, 1 mL each.

FS Calibrator 1: is prepared from sodium chloride and processed water, 12 x 3 mL.

RF Performance Verifier I and II: are prepared from processed human serum to which purified human proteins, bovine serum albumin, and preservative have been added, 5 x 3 mL each.

FS Reconstitution Diluent: is prepared from processed water, 12 x 5 mL.
